Now that we have computed the total assets and liabilities, let's now compute for the common stock using the equation in step 4. 

$$ \begin{aligned}
\text{CS} &= \text{TA} - {\text{TL}}- {\text{ARE}}\\[5pt]
&= \text{\$2,798,000} - {\text{1,195,000}}- {\text{1,368,000}}\\[5pt]
&= \underline{\underline{\textbf{\$235,000}}}
\end{aligned}$$
